{"id": 859, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对武侠片有哪些审美疲劳？", "description": "男的硬汉女的花瓶，你抢我东西，我证明自己。就酱。\r\n", "record_count": 5186, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183632OcUE4r8HNhDG6udo.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-21T11:34:44Z", "options": [{"id": 60160, "content": "总有个盖世英雄能以一敌万", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499802}, {"id": 61184, "content": "掉下山崖的几乎都没死，脸蒙纱巾的永远认不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531944}, {"id": 61185, "content": "后面有追兵，总是追到山崖边", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531944}, {"id": 60162, "content": "男主误服春药，明明有手...非要......", "image": null, "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 60163, "content": "民间知名情报组织：丐帮。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107785}, {"id": 61187, "content": "刷怪练级，后期boss打不过必开挂....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496723}, {"id": 60164, "content": "大招一定要等到最后才放……", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525937}, {"id": 60166, "content": "主角永远正义，永远正确。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 60168, "content": "全会轻功假了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465764}, {"id": 60169, "content": "一定和皇室有关", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519008}, {"id": 60170, "content": "好人一生平安，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 60684, "content": "大侠们的轻功特别好，但是，每当身后有追兵时，打死都不用轻功逃走，而是要屁颠屁颠的跑走。清闲的时候，反而会用轻功瞎遛达，真是醉了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 61452, "content": "“看掌！” “看剑！！” 嗯...直接出手不好吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522021}, {"id": 